description: Empower statistics of slices, lvaps, and algorithms

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  timestamp_ms AS "time",
  lvap_addr AS metric,
  best_mcs_prob
FROM lvap_stats
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(timestamp_ms)
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  timestamp_ms AS "time",
  lvap_addr AS metric,
  bw_shaper_mbps
FROM lvap_shaping
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(timestamp_ms)
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  timestamp_ms AS "time",
  lvap_addr AS metric,
  tx_throughput_mbps
FROM bin_stats
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(timestamp_ms)
ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT
  timestamp_ms AS "time",
  lvap_addr AS metric,
  tx_packets_per_second
FROM bin_stats
WHERE
  $__unixEpochFilter(timestamp_ms)
ORDER BY 1,2
